Tsunami da girgizar kasa a Indonesia: An samu bala'i, an kiyasta dubban mutane sun mutu
A cikin kwanaki na farko bayan girgizar kasa da ta afkawa Lombok, an gaya wa kungiyoyi masu zaman kansu na kasashen waje cewa ba a bukatar taimakon su.
Duk da cewa sama da kashi 10 cikin 100 na mutanen Lombok sun rasa gidajensu, gwamnati ba ta ga ya zama dole ta ayyana bala'i na kasa ba, wanda ya zama dole don samun taimakon kasa da kasa.
"A lokuta da dama, abin takaici, sun bayyana cewa ba su bukatar tallafin kasa da kasa, saboda haka ba abu mai sauki ba ne", in ji Selina Sambung.
Kungiyar Save the Children tana shirya tawagar da za ta kai su Palu, amma ba mu san ko za su iya yin aiki a wurin ba.
A cewar Mista Sutopo, jami'in hukumar kula da bala'i, gwamnatin Indonesia na gudanar da bincike kan halin da ake ciki a Palau domin ganin ko ya dace a dauki matakin da ya dace na hada kan kungiyoyin kasa da kasa.
Tun da yake ƙasar Indonesia tana fuskantar bala'i, ba ta da shiri sosai.
Ko da yake an gina mafaka a Aceh don tsunami, amma ba a yawan ganin su a wasu yankunan bakin teku.
Duk da gargadin tsunami, ba a kunna ƙararrawa ba a cikin Palau don faɗakar da jama'a, wanda wataƙila ya haifar da mutuwar mutane da yawa.
Harkokin sufuri tsakanin tsibiran Indonesiya da yawa suna da matsala ko da a yanayi mai kyau.
Bala'i na ƙara wahalar da abubuwa.
Asibitin da ke iyo, wanda aka kafa a Lombok don taimaka wa waɗanda suka sha wahala, yana zuwa Palu, amma zai ɗauki kwanaki uku kafin a kai wurin da aka yi sabon bala'in.
Shugaba Joko Widodo ya mai da inganta tsohuwar hanyar samar da kayayyakin kasa ta Indonesia babban abin da ya fi mayar da hankali a kamfen dinsa na neman zabe, kuma ya kashe kudade masu yawa wajen inganta hanyoyin mota da na dogo.
Amma gwamnatin Shugaba Joko, wanda ke neman sabon wa'adi a shekara mai zuwa, ta shiga cikin matsala ta kudi.
An kuma soki shugaban saboda tsananin rikici tsakanin addinai tsakanin masu ra'ayin mazan jiya Musulmi da sauran al'umma.
An kashe mutane fiye da dubu, kuma dubun dubatar mutane sun rasa gidajensu sakamakon rikici tsakanin Krista da Musulmai, da makamai masu linzami, baka da kibiyoyi da sauran bindigogi.
Bidiyo: Dan wasan Liverpool, Daniel Sturridge yana gwada kwallo a Chelsea da ci a saman kofin ƙofar
Daniel Starridge ya ceci Liverpool daga shan kashi a minti na 89 na wasan Premier da Chelsea, wanda aka yi ranar Asabar a filin wasa na Stamford Bridge.
Sturridge ya karbi wani ƙwallon ƙafa daga Jerdhan Shakiri kimanin mita 27 daga ƙofar Chelsea lokacin da tawagarsa ta yi asara da ci 1-0.
Ya koma hagu ya shiga ƙofar.
Kwallan ya tashi sosai kuma ya shiga cikin kusurwar saman raga.
Mai tsaron raga, Kep Arrisbalaga ya yi tsalle zuwa ga kwallon, amma ya yi latti.
A cikin wata hira da shafin yanar gizon LiverpoolFC.com, Sturridge ya ce: "Duk abin da ya faru shi ne samun wannan matsayi da kuma samun kwallon, 'yan wasa kamar Shaq koyaushe suna yin wasa mafi kyau don kai hari, don haka kawai na nemi in ba kaina lokaci mai yawa. "
"Na ga Kante yana zuwa, na kama ƙwallo, kuma ba na tunanin dogon lokaci, sai na shiga ƙofar".
A sakamakon rabin wasan, Chelsea ta jagoranci da ci 1-0, kwallon da dan kasar Belgium Eden Azar ya ci a minti na 25.
Dan wasan tsakiya na Chelsea, ya mayar da wasa ga Mateo Kovacic, ya tsallake tsakiyar filin zuwa rabin Liverpool.
A tsakiyar filin Kovacic ya buga wasa daya.
Sai ya ba da izinin zuwa ga Azari, wanda ya fita zuwa ƙofar.
Azar ya zarce kariya kuma daga gefen hagu ya buga bugun da aka yi wa mai tsaron gidan Liverpool Alison Becker, inda ya buga kusurwar raga.
Liverpool za ta kara da Napoli a wasan rukuni na gasar zakarun Turai a filin wasa na San Paolo da ke birnin Naples na Italiya a ranar Laraba da karfe 15:00.
Chelsea za ta buga wasan Euro League da kungiyar VideoTon a ranar Alhamis a London, kuma a karfe 15:00.
Wadanda suka mutu a tsunami a Indonesia sun kai 832
Yawan wadanda girgizar kasa da kuma tsunami da ta biyo baya suka yi a Indonesia ya kai 832, in ji Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta kasa a safiyar Lahadi.
