A wasu lokatai, wannan haɗin yana sa yanayin zafi ya yi sanyi sosai a wani yanki.
Za a ga irin wannan canjin yanayin zafi a tsakiyar Amurka a ranar Lahadi.
Akwai bambanci na kusan digiri 20 tsakanin yanayin zafi a Kansas City (Missouri) da Omaha (Nebraska), da kuma tsakanin St. Louis da De Moines (Iowa).
