Kwallon farko na Dolly Mengi ya tabbatar da nasarar kungiyar Livingston
Ta hanyar kwallo da aka zura, Livingston ya sami nasara mai ban mamaki akan Rangers. Ga babban kocin kungiyar na Scotland, Stephen Gerrard, wannan shine kashi na biyu a cikin wasanni 18.
Dukan wasan da Dolly Mengi ta buga ya daidaita kungiyar ta Gary Holt da kungiyar Hibernian a teburin wasan inda suka raba wuri na biyu.
Gwarzon Gerrard bai ci nasara ba a gasar Premier na bana, kuma a ranar Lahadi za su kara da Hearts, wanda ya kai Rangers maki takwas.
A ranar Alhamis ne Rangers za su buga wasannin gasar zakarun Turai da kungiyar Rapid ta Austria (Vienna).
Kungiyar Livingston ta ci gaba da jerin wasanninta ba tare da cin nasara ba a cikin rukunin, ta buga wasanni shida kuma ba ta ci ko daya ba tun lokacin da Holt ya maye gurbin Kenny Miller a matsayin babban kocin kungiyar.
Lokacin da aka rasa wa Livingston a wasan da ya yi da wasu 'yan wasa masu tsananin son zama
Dole ne mai horar da Holt ya yi lissafi tun daga farko. Ranger ya kasa jimrewa da matsin.
Scott Robinson ya yi nasarar tsallake layin tsaron, amma kwallo daga ƙoƙarinsa mara kyau bai fita ba. Bayan haka, mai tsaron Alan Lithgow, yana motsawa sosai, bai iya hana kwallon Cage Halkett shiga cikin raga ba.
Mai masaukin ya bar Rangers su yi wasa a gaban layin kare su, suna fatan samun hadari a lokacin da za a sake fara wasan.
Wannan shi ne yadda suka yi rashin nasarar cin kwallo mai muhimmanci.
Rangers sun ba da kyauta, kuma Livingston ya yi amfani da damar: Declan Gallagher da Robinson sun ba da Mengele, wanda ya zira kwallo daga tsakiyar.
A lokacin, Rangers sun fi kowa samun kwallon, amma ba a iya tsallakewa a tsaron da ake yi wa 'yan wasan da ke karbar bakuncin, saboda haka, mai tsaron gidan Liam Kelly bai damu ba.
A karo na biyu kuma, Kelly ya ci gaba da buga kwallo daga hannun Alfredo Morelos.
Mai tsaron ragar Rangers Allan McGregor ya ja ƙwallo daga Scott Pittman, kuma Lithgow ya yi babban aiki daga matsayi na yau da kullum.
Kwallan suna ci gaba da shiga gidan cin zarafin Livingston, amma duk hare-haren sun yi watsi da su, kuma an yi watsi da takunkumin fanareti guda biyu, daya don tayar da dan wasan da ke cikin madadin Glenn Middleton tare da Halkett, kuma na biyu don wasa da hannu.
Wani wasa mai ban mamaki  Livingston   bincike
BBC Scotland  Alasdair Lamont, rahoto daga filin wasa  Tony Makeroni Arena
Wasan wasa ne mai ban mamaki kuma kyakkyawan sakamako ga Livingston.
Dukkan 'yan wasan sun yi fice kuma sun sake wuce dukkan tsammanin, suna ci gaba da hawa zuwa gasar kwallon kafa ta Olympics.
Halin wasan su da kuma tsarin su ba su canza ba tun lokacin da suka hau saman jerin, kuma babban abin da kocin Holt ya yi shi ne ya tara wannan tawagar tun daga farko.
Akwai wasu jarumai masu kyau a cikin tawagarsa.
Kyaftin Hulkett ya ja-goranci tsaro mai kyau, kuma Menga bai bar Connor Goldson da Joe Worrall su huta ba.
Amma 'yan wasan ba su iya yin wasa ba.
Ko da yake sun yi wasa mai kyau tare da kocin Gerrard, amma ba su cika dukan tsammaninmu ba.
A minti na karshe na wasan, ba su da isasshen ikon mallakar kwallon, kuma sun sami damar wucewa ta hanyar kare kungiyar mai masaukin baki sau daya kawai.  Rangers, wanda ya sauka a tsakiyar tebur, yana da abin tunani.
Taron maraba da Erdogan a ziyarar da ya kai Köln
A ranar Asabar, 29 ga watan Satumba, lokacin da shugabannin Turkiya da Jamus suka taru don cin abincin safe, yanayi ya yi kyau, kuma shugabannin biyu suna cikin yanayi mai kyau.
Wannan shi ne rana ta karshe da shugaban kasar Erdogan ya kai ziyara Jamus domin inganta dangantaka tsakanin kasashen biyu da ke cikin kungiyar NATO  ziyarar da ta riga ta kasance da rikici.
Shugabannin kasashen sun kasa samun fahimtar juna kan batutuwan da suka shafi 'yancin dan adam, 'yancin jarida da kuma shiga Tarayyar Turai.
Bayan haka, Erdogan ya tafi Cologne don halartar bikin bude babban masallaci.
A Köln ne mafi yawan al'ummar Turkiyya da ke zaune a waje da Turkiyya.
Saboda dalilai na tsaro, 'yan sanda sun hana taron mutane dubu 25 shiga masallacin, amma magoya bayan Erdogan da dama sun yi ta yawo a kusa don ganin shugaban kasarsu.
A wannan wurin ne maƙiyan gwamnatin Erdogan suka taru, ciki har da Kurdawa, don yin tir da manufofin Erdogan da kuma shawarar gwamnatin Jamus ta gayyace shi ziyarar Jamus.
Kasancewar ra'ayoyi daban-daban a taron ya nuna irin halin da Erdogan yake ciki: yawancin Jamusawa masu asalin Turkiya suna girmama shi, yayin da wasu kuma suna ganin shi dan ta'adda ne.
Hadarin mota a titunan Deptford: motar ta yi karo da ita, ta yi sanadiyyar mutuwar wani mai hawa babur
