Rikicin da ya faru a gidan yarin Long Lartin: 'Yan sanda shida sun ji rauni
A cewar gwamnatin Long Lartin, 'yan sanda shida ne suka ji rauni a lokacin da aka yi tarzoma a gidan yarin maza na tsauraran matakan tsaro.
A ranar Lahadi ne aka fara tashin hankali a kurkukun Long Lartin na maza da ke Worcestershire, wanda ya fara da misalin karfe 9:30 na dare.
Don murkushe tashin hankali, wanda fursunoni takwas daga reshe ɗaya suka shiga, an kira ƙungiyar Tornado.
'Yan sandan sun sami rauni kaɗan a jikin su; an ba su magani a wurin.
Wani jami'in da ke kula da ayyukan kurkuku ya ce an tura ma'aikatan da aka horar musamman don su magance matsalar a kurkuku mai suna Long Lartin.
Shida daga cikinsu sun ji rauni.
Mun yi tir da amfani da karfi a cikin wannan ma'aikata, kuma a bayyane yake cewa za a mika masu laifin ga 'yan sanda kuma za a iya sauya dokar hana su yin aiki na tsawon lokaci.
A yanzu haka, Long Lartin yana ɗauke da fursunoni fiye da 500, har da wasu daga cikin masu aikata laifi mafi haɗari a ƙasar.
