Tauraron Game da kursiyai Keith Harington ya kai hari ga lalataccen namiji
Keith Harington sananne ne saboda rawar da ya taka na John Snow mai faman takobi a cikin mummunan wasan kwaikwayo na HBO na wasan kwaikwayo na Game of Thrones.
Amma, kwanan nan, dan wasan mai shekaru 31 ya yi tir da ra'ayin da ake yi na jarumin macho, yana mai cewa irin waɗannan halayen sukan sa matasa su yi tunanin cewa dole ne su kasance masu zalunci idan suna son a girmama su.
A hirarsa da jaridar The Sunday Times Culture, Keith ya ce yana ganin cewa "wani abu ya ɓace" kuma ya yi mamakin yadda za a magance matsalar ƙarancin maza a zamanin #MeToo.
Keith, wanda kwanan nan ya auri abokin aikinsa na Game of Thrones, Rose Leslie, wata budurwa mai shekaru ɗaya, ya yarda cewa "ba shi da wata damuwa game da wannan matsalar".
"Ni kaina na dauki wannan tambayar da muhimmanci: ina ne muka yi kuskure game da yadda muke ganin namiji?" in ji jarumin.
"Me yasa muke koya wa yara da suke girma cewa muna da wannan matsalar a yau?"
Keith ya yi imanin cewa talabijin na iya zama wani ɓangare na wannan tashin hankali na mazaunin da ke da guba saboda halayen da ke da ƙarfi.
Mai wasan ya ci gaba: "Mece ce 'yar haihuwa, kuma mece ce 'yar samu?"
Menene ake koyarwa a talabijin da kuma a kan titi da ke sa matasa maza su ji cewa dole ne su nuna wani bangare na namiji?
Ina tsammanin wannan shine ainihin babbar matsalar zamaninmu, kuma tambayar ita ce, ta yaya za mu iya canza wannan?
Domin akwai wani abu da ke damun matasa a yau.
A cikin hirar, ya kuma yarda cewa ba zai shiga cikin kowane prequel ko sequel na Game of Thrones ba, bayan wasan ya ƙare a lokacin bazara mai zuwa, yana mai cewa ya "ƙare daga fadace-fadace da dawakai".
Daga watan Nuwamba, Keith zai taka rawa a fim din Sam Shepard na True West, wanda ke nuna yadda mai shirya fim ɗin da ɗan'uwansa, mai fashi, suke rayuwa.
A kwanan nan, ɗan wasan ya bayyana cewa yana ganin saduwa da matarsa Rose shine mafi kyawun wasan karshe na Game of Thrones a gare shi.
"Na sadu da matata a wannan shirin, don haka ya ba ni iyalina da kuma rayuwa ta gaba", in ji ɗan wasan.
Rose ta taka rawar wasan kwaikwayo na John Snow a cikin Emmy Award-winning fantasy series.
Ma'auratan sun yi bikin auren ne a watan Yunin 2018 a gidan Leslie a Scotland.
Cutar HIV/AIDS: Kasar Sin ta ba da rahoton karuwar sabbin kamuwa da cutar da kashi 14 cikin 100
Kasar Sin ta sanar da cewa yawan mutanen da ke dauke da cutar HIV da AIDS ya karu da kashi 14 cikin dari.
A cewar jami'an kiwon lafiya, fiye da mutane 820,000 ne ke fama da wannan cuta a kasar.
A kwata na biyu na shekarar 2018 kadai, an samu sabbin mutane kusan 40,000 da suka kamu da cutar.
Yawancin sababbin cututtuka sun kamu ne ta hanyar jima'i, kuma hakan ya nuna cewa yanayin ya canja.
A al'adance, cutar HIV tana yaduwa cikin sauri a wasu yankunan kasar Sin ta hanyar jinin da aka yi wa jini.
Amma, an rage yawan masu kamuwa da cutar ta HIV ta wannan hanyar zuwa kusan babu, in ji jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin a wani taron da aka gudanar a lardin Yunnan.
A kowace shekara, adadin mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar HIV da AIDS a China yana ƙaruwa da mutane 100,000.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce a cikin al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
An cire laifukan luwadi a kasar Sin a shekarar 1997, amma har yanzu ana nuna wa LGBT wariya.
Bincike ya tabbatar da cewa saboda ra'ayoyin da suka dace na ƙasar, kashi 70-90% na maza da suke jima'i da maza suna yin aure da mata.
A yawancin lokuta, ana samun cututtuka ne saboda rashin kāriya ga waɗannan ƙalilan na jima'i.
Tun 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samar da magungunan cutar kanjamau ga kowa a matsayin wani bangare na kokarin magance matsalar.
