Jam'iyyar Labour ta musanta cewa tana shirin rage wa Birtaniya aiki na mako hudu domin biyan albashin kwana biyar
Jam'iyyar Jeremy Corbyn ta Labour za ta yi la'akari da wani tsari na musamman wanda zai sa 'yan Birtaniya su yi aiki kwana hudu a mako, amma a biya su albashi kwana biyar.
An ruwaito cewa jam'iyyar na son shugabannin kamfanoni su biya ma'aikata ajiyar da suka samu sakamakon juyin juya halin kere kere a fannin fasaha ta hanyar ba su karin hutun rana.
Hakan zai ba ma'aikatan damar samun hutun kwana uku a kan albashi ɗaya.
Majiyoyin sun ce wannan ra'ayin ya dace da tsarin tattalin arzikin jam'iyyar kuma zai taimaka wa al'ummar kasar su goyi bayan ma'aikata.
Taron Kungiyoyin kwadago ya amince da sauya zuwa mako guda na aiki domin ma'aikata su amfana daga sauyin tattalin arziki.
Wani babban jami'in jam'iyyar Labour ya shaida wa The Sunday Times cewa, ana sa ran za a sanar da sake fasalin manufofin kafin karshen shekara.
 Ba za a yi wannan ba a dare, amma aikin kwana hudu  shine burinmu, wanda ya dace da tsarin jam'iyyar na sauya daidaito a tattalin arziki don amfanin ma'aikata, da kuma dabarun masana'antu na jam'iyyar.
Jam'iyyar Labor ba ita ce ta farko da ta goyi bayan wannan ra'ayin ba, saboda Jam'iyyar Green Party ta yi alkawarin yin aiki na kwana hudu a mako tun lokacin kamfen din ta na 2017.
Amma, wannan burin ba shi da goyon bayan jam'iyyar Labour a yanzu.
Wani wakilin jam'iyyar Labour ya ce: "Aikin kwana hudu ba siyasa ba ce ta jam'iyyar kuma ba a kallon ta".
Shugaba John McDonnell ya yi amfani da taron Labor na makon da ya gabata don bayyana ra'ayinsa na juyin juya halin zamantakewar al'umma a tattalin arziki.
Mista McDonnell ya ce ya kuduri aniyar kwace ikon da ke hannun "masu zartarwa da masu cin hanci da rashawa na kamfanonin samar da wutar lantarki".
Shadow Chancellor din na shirin cewa masu hannun jari na yanzu na iya rasa duk wani rabo da suka samu, saboda gwamnatin Labor na iya yin "yanke-yanke" bisa laifukan da ake zargi.
