Menene bikin Global Citizen kuma ya yi wani abu don rage talauci?
A ranar Asabar, za a yi bikin Global Citizen Festival a birnin New York, wanda ke zama abin farin ciki a kowace shekara, inda manyan 'yan wasan ke halartar bikin, kuma manufarsu ita ce kawo ƙarshen talauci a duniya.
A shekara ta bakwai, dubban mutane suna zuwa babban filin kiwo na Central Park don bikin 'yan kasa na duniya, ba wai kawai don jin dadin wasan kwaikwayon da masu yin wasan kwaikwayon kamar Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Sean Mendes suka yi ba, amma don bayyana ainihin manufar taron: kawar da matsanancin talauci a shekarar 2030.
Bikin 'yan kasa na duniya, wanda aka kaddamar a shekarar 2012, ci gaba ne na wani shiri na duniya na yaki da talauci da kungiyar kare hakkin bil adama ta kasa da kasa ke gudanarwa, wanda ke fatan kawo karshen talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke yaki da talauci.
Don samun tikitin kyauta zuwa taron (idan ba ka shirya biyan tikitin VIP ba), dole ne ka shiga aikin sa kai ko aika imel ga shugaban duniya, yin kiran waya ko kuma yin wani abu mai ma'ana da zai taimaka wajen wayar da kan jama'a game da burin ka na kawar da talauci.
Amma yaya nasarar bikin 'yan kasa na duniya ya kasance a cikin shekaru 12 na cimma burin?
Shin ra'ayin bayar da lada ta hanyar halartar wasan kwaikwayon kyauta yana da gaske don shawo kan 'yan ƙasa su nemi kira zuwa aiki, ko kuwa wannan wani lamari ne na abin da ake kira "clictivism" inda mutane ke gaskanta cewa suna yin canji ta hanyar sanya hannu kan takarda ta kan layi ko aika saƙonni ta Twitter?
Masu shirya Global Citizen sun ce tun shekarar 2011 an yi rajistar fiye da shekaru miliyan 19 a bikin, wanda magoya bayansa suka gudanar, wadanda ke bin manufofi daban-daban.
A sakamakon wannan matakin, shugabannin duniya sun yi alkawarin samar da sama da dala biliyan 37 da za su taimaka wa mutane biliyan 2.25 nan da shekara ta 2030.
A farkon shekarar 2018, kungiyar ta bayyana alkawura 390 da kuma sanarwar da aka yi sakamakon ayyukanta, wanda akalla dala biliyan 10 daga cikinsu an riga an biya ko kuma an tara su.
Ƙungiyar ta kimanta cewa, tallafin da aka bayar ya taimaka wa mutane kusan miliyan 649 a dukan duniya.
Daya daga cikin manyan alkawuran da aka yi shi ne mai suna The Power of Nutrition, wanda wani kungiya na masu zuba jari da masu kirkirar ayyuka a Burtaniya da ke da alhakin taimaka wa yara su samu nasarorin da suka dace, ta yi alkawarin bayar da dala miliyan 35 ga kasar Rwanda domin taimakawa wajen kawo karshen rashin abinci mai gina jiki a yankin, bayan karbar tweets sama da 4,700 daga masu shiga Global Citizens.
"Tare da goyon bayan gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu bayar da tallafi, gwamnatocin kasa da kuma 'yan kasa na duniya kamar ku, za mu iya kawo rashin adalci na rashin abinci mai gina jiki a tarihin da ya gabata", in ji jakadan Power of Nutrition Tracy Ullman a lokacin wani taron raye-raye a London a watan Afrilu na shekarar 2018.
Kungiyar ta kuma ce bayan an dauki mataki sama da 5,000 na neman Birtaniya ta inganta abinci mai gina jiki ga mata da yara, gwamnati ta sanar da kudade ga shirin Ƙarfin Abinci wanda zai kai mata da yara miliyan 5 ta hanyar ayyukan inganta abinci mai gina jiki.
A amsa ga tambayar da ake yawan yi a shafin yanar gizon bikin: Me ya sa kuke ganin za mu iya kawar da matsanancin talauci?
Masu shirya shirin Global citizen sun amsa cewa: Za mu yi tafiya mai tsawo da wahala, inda za mu yi tuntuɓe da faduwa a wasu lokutan.
Amma kamar yadda yake a cikin manyan ƙungiyoyin 'yancin jama'a da na nuna bambanci, za mu yi nasara domin tare muna da ƙarfi.
Janet Jackson, Weekend, Sean Mendes, Cardi B, Janelle Monet  waɗannan su ne wasu daga cikin masu yin wasan kwaikwayon da za su yi a taron na wannan shekara a New York, kuma Deborah-Lee Ferness da Hugh Jackman ne za su gabatar da shi.
Amurka na iya amfani da rundunar sojin ruwan ta 'Blockout' don hana fitar da makamashin Rasha: Ministan cikin gida
Sakataren harkokin cikin gida na Amurka Ryan Zinke ya bayyana cewa Washington na iya idan ya cancanta ta nemi taimakon rundunar sojan ruwanta don hana masu samar da makamashi na Rasha shiga kasuwannin, ciki har da Gabas ta Tsakiya.
Zinke ya yi ikirarin cewa kasancewar Rasha a Syria, musamman inda take aiki bisa gayyatar gwamnatin da ta dace, wata hujja ce don bincika sabbin kasuwannin makamashi.
"Ina ganin dalilin da ya sa suke Gabas ta Tsakiya shi ne domin suna son su yi kasuwanci da makamashi kamar yadda suke yi a gabashin Turai, a kudancin Turai", in ji shi.
Kuma a cewar jami'in, akwai wasu hanyoyi da kuma hanyoyin magance wannan matsalar.
"Amurka tare da rundunar sojin ruwanmu za su iya tabbatar da bude hanyoyin ruwa, kuma idan ya zama dole, su rufe su don kada makamashin su shiga kasuwa", in ji ministan.
Zinke ya yi magana ga mahalarta taron da kungiyar Consumer Energy Alliance, wata kungiya mai zaman kanta da ke bayyana kanta a matsayin 'muryar masu amfani da makamashi' a Amurka.
Daga nan sai ya kwatanta yadda Washington ke hulda da Rasha da Iran, inda ya ce sun yi kama da juna.
"Tsarin tattalin arzikin Iran da Rasha ya fi ko kasa da amfani da mai da maye", in ji ministan, yana mai kiran Rasha "tauraro guda daya", wanda tattalin arzikinsa ya dogara da man fetur.
An yi maganganun ne saboda gwamnatin Trump ta sanya wa kanta manufar kara fitar da iskar gas dinta mai narkewa zuwa Turai, ta maye gurbin Rasha da ke ba da wani zaɓi mai rahusa ga masu amfani da Turai.
Don haka jami'an gwamnatin Trump, ciki har da shugaban Amurka Donald Trump, suna kokarin shawo kan Jamus ta fice daga aikin samar da bututun mai mai suna Nord Stream-2 wanda Trump ya ce ya sa Berlin ta zama fursuna a hannun Moscow.
A Moscow an sha jaddada cewa aikin Nord Stream-2 mai darajar dala biliyan 11, wanda ya kamata ya ninka ƙarfin ƙarfin wutar lantarki na yanzu zuwa mita biliyan 110, shiri ne na tattalin arziki.
Kremlin ya yi ikirarin cewa tsayayyar da Washington ke yi wa wannan aikin na da nasaba da dalilai na tattalin arziki kuma misali ne na rashin gaskiya.
"Ina mai jaddada cewa muna da ra'ayin cewa ba za a iya amfani da makamashi a matsayin kayan aiki ba don matsa lamba kuma ya kamata masu amfani su sami damar zaɓar masu samar da su", in ji Ministan makamashin Rasha Alexander Novak bayan ganawarsa da Ministan makamashin Amurka Rick Perry a watan Satumba a Moscow.
Matsayin Amurka ya haifar da mummunan martani daga Jamus, wanda ya tabbatar da jajircewarsa ga aikin.
Masu sana'ar Jamus a madadin kungiyar masana'antar Jamus (BDI), sun bukaci Amurka da ta yi nesa da manufofin makamashi na EU da yarjejeniyar biyu tsakanin Berlin da Moscow.
"Lokacin da wata kasa ta uku ta shiga cikin samar da makamashi, wannan babbar matsala ce", in ji Dieter Kempf, shugaban kungiyar masana'antu ta Jamus (BDI), bayan ganawar da Shugabar Jamus Angela Merkel da Shugaba na Rasha Vladimir Putin suka yi kwanan nan.
Sanata Elizabeth Warren daga Massachusetts za ta yi nazari sosai kan yadda za ta yi takarar shugaban kasa a shekarar 2020
Sanata Elizabeth Warren daga jihar Massachusetts ta ce a ranar Asabar za ta yi nazari sosai kan yadda za ta tsaya takarar shugaban kasa bayan zaben fidda gwani.
A taron majalisar dattijai a garin Holyoke, Massachusetts, Warren ta tabbatar da cewa za ta yi la'akari da shiga cikin zaben.
"Lokaci ya yi da mata za su je Washington su gyara gwamnatinmu da ta lalace, kuma don yin hakan, ana bukatar mace a kan gaba", in ji Warren The Hill.
"Bayan 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zan yi la'akari sosai da neman takarar shugaban kasa".
Warren ta ce, "Sai dai shugaban kasa Donald Trump yana kai wannan gundumar cikin hanyar da ba ta dace ba".
"Ina matukar damuwa da abin da Donald Trump ke yi wa dimokiradiyarmu", in ji ta.
Warren ya kasance mai sukar Trump da kuma wanda ya tsaya takara a matsayin babban alkalin shari'a Brett Kavanaugh.
A cikin wata sanarwa ta Twitter a ranar Juma'a, Warren ta rubuta cewa: "Tabbas, muna bukatar binciken FBI kafin mu fara jefa kuri'a".
Amma, wani zabe da aka fitar a ranar Alhamis ya nuna cewa yawancin masu jefa kuri'a ba su yi tunanin Warren ta tsaya takara a 2020 ba.
A cewar wani bincike da Cibiyar Nazarin Siyasa ta Jami'ar Suffolk/Boston Globe ta yi, kashi 58 cikin 100 na masu jefa kuri'a a Massachusetts sun ce bai kamata a zabi sanata ba.
Akasin haka, kashi 32 cikin 100 na mutanen da aka yi wa tambayoyi suna goyon bayan shirin ta.
Binciken ya nuna cewa yawan jama'a sun fi goyon bayan tsohon gwamna Deval Patrick, kashi 38 cikin dari na goyon bayan yiwuwar shi shiga zaben, yayin da kashi 48 cikin dari suka nuna adawa.
Sauran sanannun sunayen 'yan Democrat da aka tattauna a kan hangen nesa na 2020 sun hada da tsohon mataimakin shugaban kasa Joe Biden da Sanata Bernie Sanders na Vermont.
Biden ya ce zai yanke shawara a watan Janairu, in ji Associated Press.
Sarah Palin ta bayyana yadda Trac Palin ya kamu da ciwon tashin hankali bayan da ya ji rauni a taron masu kada kuri'ar Donald Trump
Track Palin, mai shekara 26, ya shiga aikin soja a watan Satumba, ya yi shekara ɗaya a ƙasar Iraki.
An kama shi kuma an tuhume shi da cin zarafin cikin gida a daren Litinin.
"Ɗana da ya dawo gida yana fuskantar irin yanayin da sauran iyalan da ke fama da cutar PTSD da suka ji rauni, kuma sojojinmu suna dawowa da raunuka", in ji ta a wani taro da Donald Trump a Tulsa, Oklahoma.
Palin ta kira wannan kama da "karin haske" kuma ta ce game da ɗanta da sauran tsoffin sojin yakin, "suna dawowa da wasu, masu tsananin damuwa, suna mamakin ko ana girmama su kamar yadda suka girmama ƙasarsu".
An kama Track Palin a ranar Litinin a Vasilla, Alaska, kuma an tuhume shi da cin zarafin mata a cikin gida, ta hanyar shiga cikin tashin hankali da kuma riƙe da makami yayin da yake cikin maye, a cewar Dan Bennett, mai magana da yawun sashen 'yan sanda na Vasilla.
Jihohi 18 da D.C. sun goyi bayan sabon tsarin neman mafaka
Jihohi 18 da D.C. sun goyi bayan shigar da kara a shari'a kan sabuwar manufar Amurka da ta hana ba da mafaka ga wadanda suka tsere ko kuma wadanda ake zalunta a cikin gida.
NBC News ta ruwaito cewa, wakilan jihohi da gundumomi 18 sun gabatar da takardar bincike a Washington ranar Juma'a daga mai ba da shawara kan kotu game da goyon bayan mai neman mafaka da ke kalubalantar manufofinsa.
Ba a bayyana cikakken sunan mai shigar da kara a shari'ar Grace da Sessions da kungiyar kare hakkin bil adama ta Amurka ta shigar a watan Agusta kan dokar tarayya ba.
Wata mata ta yi ikirarin cewa mijinta ne da 'ya'yansa maza, wadanda ke cikin kungiyar masu aikata laifuka, sun yi mata mummunan aiki, amma a ranar 20 ga watan Yuli jami'an Amurka sun ki amincewa da bukatar ta na neman mafaka.
An kama ta a Texas.
Lauyoyin jihohi da ke goyon bayan Grace sun ce El Salvador, Honduras da Guatemala suna da yawan neman mafaka a Amurka, a matsayin kasashen da ke fuskantar matsalolin da suka shafi kungiyoyin masu aikata laifi da kuma tashin hankali a cikin gida.
Sabuwar manufar Amurka game da mafaka ta soke shawarar da Majalisar 'Yan Gudanar da Shige da Fice ta yi a shekarar 2014 wanda ya bai wa baƙi marasa tushe damar neman mafaka.
Babban Lauyan D.C. Carl Racine ya ce a cikin wata sanarwa a ranar Juma'a cewa sabuwar manufar "ta yi watsi da shekarun da suka gabata na amfani da dokokin jihohi, tarayya da na kasa da kasa".
"Dokar tarayya ta bukaci a bincika duk wani neman mafaka bisa ga takamaiman hujjoji da kuma yanayin da ake nema, kuma wannan haramcin ya saɓa wa wannan ƙa'ida", in ji sanarwar mai ba da shawara.
Lauyoyi sun kuma yi ikirarin cewa dokar hana shigo da baƙi na cutar da tattalin arzikin Amurka, suna mai jaddada cewa wannan rukunin 'yan ƙasa ne da ke da damar zama' yan kasuwa kuma suna samar da ma'aikata .
A watan Yuni, Babban Lauyan Jiha Jeff Sessions ya ba da umarnin cewa alƙalan 'yan gudun hijira ba za su ƙara ba da mafaka ga waɗanda suka tsere daga cin zarafin gida ko na 'yan bindiga ba.
"Za a ba da mafaka ga waɗanda suka bar ƙasarsu saboda tsanantawa ko tsoron tsoratarwa saboda launin fata, addini, ƙasa, ko kuma takamaiman rukuni na zamantakewa ko ra'ayi na siyasa", in ji Sashens a cikin sanarwar da ya fitar a ranar 11 ga Yuni.
Ba a taɓa tsara wannan kayan aiki don magance dukan matsaloli ba, har ma da manyan matsalolin da mutane suke fuskanta a kowace rana a dukan duniya.
