Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da "harin" da aka kai ta hanyar "tallan farfaganda".
Mako guda bayan da wata jaridar kasar Sin ta wallafa wani talla mai shafi hudu a wata jaridar Amurka da ke bayyana amfanin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China, jakadan Amurka a China ya zargi Beijing da amfani da kafofin yada labarai na Amurka wajen yada farfaganda.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi nuni da wani shafin da ake biyan kudi na Des Moines Register China Daily, babban jaridar kasuwanci a jihar Iowa, a ranar Laraba, inda ya zargi kasar Sin da kokarin tsoma baki a zaben da za a yi a ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, wanda kasar Sin ta musanta.
Zargin da Trump ya yi na cewa Beijing na kokarin tsoma baki a zaben Amurka, ya tabbatar da wani abu da jami'an Amurka suka fada wa kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters: cewa sabon mataki ya zo ne a cikin yakin da Washington ke karawa na matsa lamba kan kasar Sin.
Yayin da ya zama al'ada ga gwamnatocin kasashen waje su sanya tallace-tallace don inganta kasuwanci, Beijing da Washington a halin yanzu suna cikin yanayin ƙaruwar yaƙin cinikayya, wanda ke haifar da su daidaita haraji kan shigo da ƙasashensu.
Tarifin da China ta mayar a farkon yakin cinikayya na da burin ta yi wa masu fitar da kayayyaki a jihohi kamar Iowa, wadanda ke goyon bayan jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump, in ji masana na China da na Amurka.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a kasar Sin kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa, babban mai fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa kasar Sin, ya yi ikirarin cewa Beijing ta yi wa ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da 'yan kasuwa lahani.
China, in ji Branstad a wata kasida da aka buga a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register ta ranar Lahadi, "yanzu tana ninka wannan cin zarafin ta hanyar sanya tallace-tallace na farfaganda a cikin 'yan jaridarmu masu 'yanci".
"A cikin yada farfagandarsu, gwamnatin kasar Sin tana amfani da al'adun Amurka na 'yancin magana da kuma 'yancin jarida ta hanyar biyan kuɗi da kuma sanya talla a cikin Des Moines Register", in ji Branstad.
"Amma a kantunan jaridu a nan titunan Beijing, ba za ku ji muryoyin masu ra'ayi daban-daban ba kuma ba za ku ga ra'ayoyi iri-iri da 'yan kasar Sin za su iya fahimta ba idan suka ji game da siyasa ta tattalin arziki na kasar Sin, saboda kafofin watsa labarai na gida suna karkashin kulawar jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin", in ji shi.
Ya kuma kara da cewa, daya daga cikin shahararrun jaridun kasar Sin ta yi watsi da shawarar da ta bayar na buga labarinsa, duk da cewa bai bayyana ainihin sunan jaridar ba.
Masu sharhi sun gargadi: da rikici na Kavanaugh ' yan Republican suna tura mata masu zabe a gaban lokacin tsaka-tsaki
Yawancin manyan 'yan Republican sun fi son tsayawa gefe kuma suna goyon bayan takarar babban alkalin shari'a Brett Kavanaugh, duk da wasu zarge-zargen cin zarafin jima'i, masu sharhi sun yi gargadin cewa akwai mummunan martani, musamman daga mata, wanda zai iya tasiri a kan zaɓen da ke tafe.
Tashin hankali game da wannan lamarin ya yi zafi sosai, kuma yawancin 'yan Republican sun bayyana cewa suna son ci gaba da jefa kuri'a.
Ba za a iya komawa ga irin wannan abu ba, "in ji Grant Rieher, Farfesa a fannin ilimin siyasa a Makarantar Maxwell a Jami'ar Syracuse, a cikin wani labarin da ya wallafa a ranar Asabar.
Rieher ya yi shakkar cewa ƙoƙarin da Sanata Jeff Flake (R-Arizona) ya yi na gudanar da binciken FBI a minti na ƙarshe zai isa ya kwantar da hankalin masu jefa kuri'a.
"Mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru jiya ba, ba za su manta da shi ba gobe ko kuma a watan Nuwamba", in ji Karin Jean-Pierre, babban mai ba da shawara kuma mai magana da yawun ƙungiyar ci gaba ta MoveOn ga jaridar Washington, D.C.
Masu zanga-zangar sun yi ihu da "Nuwamba gaba!" a gaban majalisar dattawa a safiyar Juma'a, yayin da 'yan Republican da ke kula da kwamitin shari'a suka yanke shawarar gabatar da Kavanaugh, duk da shaidar Dr. Christine Blasey Ford, in ji Mic.
"Himma da himma na dimokiradiyya za su wuce gona da iri", in ji Stu Rotenberg, wani masanin siyasa wanda ba ya goyon bayan jam'iyya, a shafinsa na labarai.
Mutane suna cewa, yanayin ya riga ya yi muni sosai, kuma gaskiya ne.
Amma abubuwa na iya zama mafi muni, musamman ga mata masu jefa kuri'a a cikin yankunan karkara da kuma matasa masu jefa kuri'a, masu shekaru 18 zuwa 29, waɗanda, ko da yake ba sa son shugaban ƙasa, sau da yawa ba sa jefa kuri'a.
Tun kafin Ford ta yi shaida a fili game da dan takarar babban alkalin kotun, inda ta zarge shi da cin zarafin mata, manazarta sun yi hasashen cewa idan 'yan Republican suka amince da takarar, wannan matakin na iya haifar da martani.
"Wannan ya riga ya zama rikici ga jam'iyyar Republican", in ji Michael Steele, tsohon shugaban kwamitin Republican na kasa, a farkon makon da ya gabata, kamar yadda NBC News ta ruwaito.
"Ba wai kawai batun batun kuri'ar kwamitin ba ne ko kuma kuri'ar karshe ko kuma ko Kavanaugh ya zauna a kan kujera, amma kuma yadda 'yan Republican ke bi da shi, yadda suke ji game da shi", in ji Guy Cecil, darektan Priorities USA, wani rukuni da ke taimakawa wajen zaben 'yan Democrat, ga tashar labarai.
Amma dai, jama'ar Amirka sun rarrabu kan ko su amince da Ford ko Kavanaugh, kuma sun fi karkata ga na biyun.
Wani sabon binciken YouGov ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin 100 na masu amsa sun tabbata ko kuma sun yi imani da abin da Ford ya ce, yayin da kashi 35 cikin 100 suka ce sun tabbata ko kuma sun yi imani da Kavanaugh.
Bugu da ƙari, kashi 38 cikin ɗari sun yi imanin cewa Kavanaugh ya yi ƙarya ko kuma ya yi ƙarya a lokacin da yake ba da shaida, yayin da kashi 30 cikin ɗari ne kawai suka ce haka game da Ford.
A kan bukatar Flake, FBI tana binciken tuhumar da Ford ya yi, da kuma akalla wani mai tuhumar  Deborah Ramirez, in ji The Guardian.
A makon da ya gabata, Ford ta shaida a gaban kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa cewa Kawano, yayin da yake cikin maye, ya yi mata hari lokacin da take 'yar shekara 17.
Ramirez ta yi ikirarin cewa dan takarar babban alkalin kotun ya nuna mata al'aurarsa a wani biki a lokacin da take karatu a jami'ar Yale a shekarun 1980.
Wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo na shirin kaddamar da sabuwar intanet ga Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo, ya kafa wani kamfanin farawa da zai yi takara da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Aikin karshe na almara na fasaha, Inrupt, kamfani ne da aka kafa a kan hanyar sadarwa ta Berners-Lee Solid.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda za su adana bayanan su da kuma waɗanne mutane za su ba da damar shiga waɗanne bayanai.
A wata hira ta musamman da Fast Company Berners-Lee ya yi da cewa manufar Inrupt ita ce ta mallaki duniya.
"Ya kamata mu yi shi yanzu", in ji shi game da farawar sa.
Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi.
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar Solid, wanda ke bawa mutane damar ƙirƙirar nasu  ɗakunan ajiya na kan layi ko POD.
Za ka iya samun jerin lambobin sadarwa, da kuma kalandarka, da kuma laburaren kiɗa da kuma wasu kayan aiki na sana'a da na sirri.
Aikace-aikacen yana aiki ne bisa ka'idar Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify  ana iya amfani da su duka a cikin burauzar yanar gizo guda kuma a lokaci guda.
Abin da ke sa ajiyar bayanan sirri ta kan layi ta kasance ta musamman shi ne, mai amfani ne yake sarrafa shi, kuma yana iya samun duk wani bayani da yake bukata.
Kamfanin ya kira wannan ka'idar "ci gaba da samun dama ta hanyar bayanai".
A cewar Shugaba John Bruce, manufar Inrupt ita ce, kamfanin ya samar da albarkatu, aiyuka da kuma ƙwarewar da ta dace don sanya Solid ya zama mai amfani ga kowa.
A halin yanzu, kamfanin ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, dandamali na tsaro wanda IBM ta saya, da wasu masu haɓaka na yau da kullun waɗanda aka kulla yarjejeniya tare da su don yin aiki akan aikin, da kuma ƙungiyar masu shirye-shiryen sa kai.
Farawa daga wannan makon, masu fasahar zamani a duk duniya za su iya gina nasu aikace-aikacen da aka rarraba ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke cikin shafin yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba su tattauna da Facebook da Google ba game da ko ya kamata kamfanin ya yi wasu canje-canje masu ban mamaki da za su kawo sauyi ga tsarin kasuwancin su baki daya cikin dare.
"Ba mu tambayar su izini".
A cikin wani sakon da ya wallafa a Medium a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa, manufar Inrupt ita ce samar da wutar lantarki da kuma tsarin halittu don kare inganci da ingancin sabuwar hanyar sadarwa da aka gina a kan Solid.
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya sake fasalin Intanet ta hanyar kafa World Wide Web Consortium a MIT.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ta yi tasiri sosai a muhawara game da tsaka tsaki a kan intanet.
Ko da lokacin da ya kaddamar da Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai kasance wanda ya kafa kuma darektan ƙungiyar World Wide Web, Gidauniyar Intanet da Cibiyar Bayanai ta Bude.
"Ina da kyakkyawan fata game da wannan zamanin na Intanet", in ji Berners-Lee.
Bernard Vann: wani ma'aikacin coci wanda aka ba da kyautar Victoria a lokacin yakin duniya na farko
A tarihin cocin Ingila, firist guda ne kawai ya sami kyautar Victoria Cross a lokacin yakin duniya na farko, kuma an yi bikin a garinsu bayan shekaru 100.
An ba da wannan lambar yabo ga Sub-Colonel Bernard Vann a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918 don shiga cikin harin da aka kai wa Bellenglish da Leucor.
Abin baƙin ciki, wani dan bindiga ya kashe shi bayan kwana huɗu, ba tare da ya san cewa ya sami lambar yabo mafi girma na Birtaniya ba.
An bude abin tunawa da wannan taron ne da jikokinsa biyu a wani biki a Rushden, Northamptonshire, ranar Asabar.
Ɗaya daga cikin jikokinsa, Michael Vann, ya ce abin mamaki ne cewa an buɗe abin tunawa daidai shekaru 100 bayan da kakansa ya sami lambar yabo.
A cewar jaridar London a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, wani dan kwamitin soja mai suna Lieutenant Colonel Vann ya kai tawagarsa ta hanyar tashar Saint-Canthen a cikin wani hazo mai yawa da kuma wuta mai karfi na bindigogi da bindigogi.
Daga baya ya yi tsalle zuwa layin wuta kuma tare da "ƙarfin gwiwa" ya jagoranci rukuni gaba, sannan ya jefa bindiga ta filin tare da hannu ɗaya, ya kashe sojoji uku na rukunin.
An kashe Subcolonel Vann da wani dan damfara na Jamus a ranar 4 ga Oktoba, 1918  fiye da wata daya kafin yakin ya ƙare.
Michael Vann, wani jikoki mai shekaru 72, ya ce ba zai iya yin irin wannan aikin jarumtaka ba, amma abin ya ba shi ta'aziyya.
Shi da ɗan'uwansa Dr. James Vann sun kuma kafa kambi bayan bikin, wanda ƙungiyar 'yan wasan matasa ta Imperial Brentwood ta gudanar.
Michael Vann ya ce yana da matukar girmamawa ya halarci bikin, ya kuma kara da cewa, "yawan jarumin na gaskiya ya nuna goyon bayan da mutane da dama za su bayar".
