Tom Daly ya ji kamar bai isa ba saboda yadda yake so
Tom Daly, mai shiga cikin ruwa a gasar Olympics ya ce ya girma yana jin cewa shi ne mafi muni saboda jima'i, amma wannan shi ne ya ba shi dalili na samun nasara.
Dan wasan mai shekara 24 ya bayyana cewa bai fahimci cewa ba kowa bane kamarsa ba har sai da ya shiga makarantar sakandare.
A cikin shirin farko na Radio 4 Desert Island Discs, wanda Lauren Lavern ta gabatar, ya ce ya yi magana game da 'yancin gay don ba wa wasu "bege".
Ya kuma ce ya daina damuwa da gasar Olympics bayan ya haifi jariri.
Mai gabatar da shirin Kirsty Young mai shekaru da yawa ya dauki hutun watanni saboda rashin lafiya.
Daly, wanda ya yi baƙo a shirin LaVern, ya ce ya ji "ƙasa fiye da kowane ɗayan takwarorinsa" saboda ba a yarda da halayensa na jima'i a cikin al'umma ba, ga yara maza da mata.
Ya ce, "Har zuwa yau, wannan jin daɗi da rashin cancanta na gaskiya ne, amma sun ba ni ƙarfi, kuma na sami nasara".
Yana son ya tabbatar da cewa yana da muhimmanci don kada ya sa kowa ya yi baƙin ciki idan suka gano cewa shi mai son jima'i ne.
Gwarzon dan wasan Olympics sau biyu ya zama sanannen mai fafutukar LGBT kuma a jawabinsa a wasannin Commonwealth da aka yi a Australia a wannan shekarar ya bukaci kasashen da su kawar da aikata laifuka na luwadi.
Ya ce ya yi wannan furucin ne saboda yana da sa'a ya rayu a bayyane, ba tare da sakamako ba, kuma yana son ya ba wa wasu "bege".
Gwarzon dan wasan duniya sau uku ya ce yana da "fargaba" game da wani mutum, darektan fim din Amurka Dustin Lance Black, wanda ya sadu da shi a shekarar 2013.
A shekarar da ta gabata, Daly ya auri wani dan wasan da ya lashe kyautar Oscar wanda ya girme shi da shekara 20, amma ya ce bambancin shekaru bai taba zama matsala ba.
"Idan akwai abubuwa da yawa da ke faruwa a rayuwarka a wannan lokacin, "ya je gasar Olympics ta farko yana da shekara 14, kuma mahaifinsa ya mutu daga ciwon daji shekaru uku bayan haka, "yana da wuya a sami wani ɗan shekara ɗaya wanda ke da irin wannan bambancin rayuwa.
Sun zama iyaye a watan Yuni, kuma suka haifi ɗa da suka kira Robert Ray Black Daley, kuma Daley ya ce "duk yadda yake kallon duniya" ya canza.
"Idan kun tambaye ni a bara, zan ce ina bukatar lashe lambar zinare", in ji dan wasan.
Amma akwai abubuwa da suka fi zinare na Olympics muhimmanci.
Na samu lambar zinare ta gasar Olympics da Robbie.
An sa wa ɗansa suna ne don girmama mahaifinsa Robert, wanda ya mutu a shekara ta 2011 yana da shekaru 40 daga ciwon kwakwalwa.
Daly ya bayyana cewa mahaifinsa bai yarda da cewa yana mutuwa ba, kuma daya daga cikin abubuwan da ya nema na karshe shine tikiti na gaba don gasar London 2012.
"Ba zan iya ce masa 'Baba' ba, ba za ka kasance a wurin ba, kuma ba za ka iya zama a jere na gaba ba", in ji Daly.
"Na riƙe hannunsa lokacin da ya daina numfashi, kuma sai da ya daina numfashi ne na fahimci cewa ba shi da nasara", in ji dan wasan.
A shekara mai zuwa, Daly ya shiga gasar Olympics ta 2012 kuma ya lashe tagulla.
"Na san cewa wannan shine abin da nake fata a rayuwata, yin iyo a gaban jama'a a wasannin Olympics, ba abin da ya fi wannan kyau", in ji shi.
Wannan kuma ya ba shi kwarin gwiwa don zaɓar waƙar da ya fi so  Proud by Heather Small  wanda ya taimaka masa shirya don wasannin Olympics kuma har yanzu yana son shi.
