Mickelson, wanda ba shi da kyau, ya buga gasar Ryder Cup a ranar Asabar.
Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson zai kafa tarihi a ranar Lahadi, bayan da ya buga wasansa na 47 a gasar Ryder Cup, amma zai yi kokarin karawa da shi don kaucewa wani mummunan yanayi.
Mickelson, wanda ya buga wasan karo na 12 a gasar, ya samu nasarar buga wasan ne a ranar Asabar da kyaftin dinsa Jim Furyck ya buga masa kwallo hudu da hudu.
Maimakon kasancewa a tsakiyar al'amuran kamar yadda ya saba a Amurka, babban gwarzon wasan sau biyar ya raba ranarsa tsakanin kallon wasan da kuma aiki a kan wasan da yake yi a filin wasa da fatan gyara abin da ke damunsa.
Ba a taɓa samun sahun kai tsaye ba, har ma a lokacin da yake kan gaba a aikinsa, ɗan wasan mai shekaru 48 ba shi da kyakkyawan takara don tsananin hanyar Le Golf National, inda dogon raf ɗin ke azabtar da rashin daidaito.
Kuma idan hanya kanta ba ta da ban tsoro, Mickelson a wasa na tara a ranar Lahadi zai yi wasa da dan wasan British Open na gaskiya Francesco Molinari, wanda ya hada kai da sabon shiga Tommy Fleetwood don lashe wasanni hudu a wannan makon.
Idan 'yan wasan Amurka, da suka yi rashin nasara da maki hudu a wasanni 12 na wasan kwaikwayo, suka fara wasa da kyau, wasan Mickelson zai iya zama mai yanke hukunci.
