Yana son ya kasance a wurin tare da kowa.
A ranar Lahadi, Mickelson zai doke rikodin Nick Fold da ya kafa a gasar cin kofin Ryder.
Wannan zai iya kawo karshen aikinsa a gasar Ryder Cup, wanda bai taba yin nasara ba.
Mickelson yana da nasara 18, ya ci 20 kuma ya tashi bakwai, kodayake Ferik ya ce kasancewarsa ya taimaka wa tawagar sosai.
"Yana da ban dariya, mai ba'a, mai hankali, yana son yin wa mutane dariya, kuma babban mutum ne da yake da sha'awa", in ji shi.
