Ronaldo ya musanta zargin fyade, kuma lauyoyinsa suna shirin kai karar wata mujallar Jamus
Cristiano Ronaldo ya musanta zargin fyade da ake yi masa, yana mai cewa "labarai ne na karya" kuma yana mai cewa mutane suna son su yi amfani da sunansa don su samu kuɗi.
Lauyoyinsa suna shirin kai karar jaridar labarai ta Spiegel ta Jamus, wadda ta wallafa zargin da ake yi wa dan wasan.
An zargi dan wasan Portugal da Juventus da yiwa wata 'yar Amurka mai suna Catherine Majorga fyade, wanda ake zargin ya faru ne a wani dakin otal a Las Vegas a shekarar 2009.
