Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a ƙasar Indonesia
A kalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu sakamakon girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta afkawa garin Palu na Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu, a cewar jami'ai.
Saboda matsalar sadarwa, masu aikin ceto ba su iya samun wani bayani daga Donggala, wani yanki da ke arewacin Palu, wanda ke kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.5.
An kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 daga garin Palu.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palau da Donggala da ke tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palau  babban birnin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi, wanda ke ƙarshen kunkuntar bakin teku a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da yawan jama'a 379,800 (bayanai na 2017).
A lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka faru, birnin yana bikin cika shekara 40.
Donggala  gundumar ce da ke kan iyakar bakin teku mai nisan kilomita 300 (180 mil) a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Yankin, yanki ne mafi ƙanƙanta fiye da lardin, a cikin 2017 ya ƙunshi mutane 299,200.
Kamun kifi da noma sune tushen tattalin arzikin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi, musamman yankin bakin teku na Donggala.
Ma'adinan nickel ma yana da mahimmanci ga tattalin arzikin lardin, amma galibi yana da hankali a Morali, a gefen tekun Sulawesi.
Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta Indonesiya ta ce a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, tsunami sun yi wa Palu da Donggala barazana sosai.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗarurruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Tsunami ya kuma auku a yammacin Donggala a shekarar 1996, inda mutane tara suka mutu.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ke cikin Tekun Fasifik, kuma tana yawan fuskantar girgizar ƙasa.
Ga wasu daga cikin manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka auku a shekarun baya bayan nan:
2004: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesia a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga watan Disamba ta haifar da tsunami da ya afkawa kasashe 14 wanda ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta yi ta ci gaba a gabar yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Mutane da yawa sun mutu a tsibirin Nias da ke bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 6.8 ta afkawa kudu da Java, tsibirin da ke da yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta haifar da tsunami da ya afkawa gaɓar tekun kudu, wanda ya kashe mutane kusan 700.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.6 ta afku a birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin Yammacin Sumatra.
Mutane sama da 1,100 suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.5 ta afku a daya daga cikin tsibirin Mentawai da ke kusa da Sumatra, ta haifar da tsunami mai tsawon mita 10, wanda ya lalata ƙauyuka da dama kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 300.
2016: Wani girgizar kasa mai rauni ta afkawa gundumar Pidi Jaya a Aceh, inda ta haifar da bala'i da fargaba yayin da mutane ke tunawa da mummunar girgizar kasa da tsunami na 2004.
Ba a yi tsunami ba, amma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu a sakamakon rushewar gine-gine.
2018: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok na Indonesia, inda ta yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane sama da 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ƙasa ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma dubban masu yawon bude ido sun kasance a ƙarƙashin kango na ɗan lokaci.
